  </p>

  <p>
    Alternatively, using <ref addr="algm-001K" href="algm-001K.xml" taxon="Construction"></ref>, we may compose two adjunctions to first <link href="algm-001K.xml" type="local" addr="algm-001K" title="Separation of presheaf">separate</link> the presheaf, and then perform the plus construction. By uniqueness of adjunction these two constructions are equivalent.
  </p>
